BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: High Park Yoga
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/high-park-yoga/
UID:event_313602466@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260321T023352Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260322T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260322T110000
SUMMARY:Wild Breath Live on Zoom
DESCRIPTION:High Park Yoga\nI know so many of you enjoy the extended\, ryt
 hmic breathwork at the end of my yoga classes. Well\, here is your chance 
 to continue harnessing the power of your breath guided by my patner Steve.
 \n\n**\\*\\*You must [sign up for free on Calendly via this link](https://
 calendly.com/breathinginnature/wild-breath) BEFORE the class to receive th
 e Zoom link\\*\\***\n\n### What's the Wild Breath?\n\nOur breath is our mo
 st powerful healing tool & the energetic link between our mind\, body\, he
 art and spirit.\nIn this free\, one hour class guided by Steve live on Zoo
 m you will use your breath to achieve a deep state of meditation and wellb
 eing. Breathing to the beats of the music\, you unlock the power within yo
 u to reduce stress and inflammation\, boost creativity\, release trapped e
 motions\, gain clarity and return to your true Self.\n\n**What you'll need
 :**\n\n* [Sign up for free on Calendly via this link](https://calendly.com
 /breathinginnature/wild-breath) **BEFORE** the class to receive the Zoom l
 ink\n* Good quality headphones or stereo system\n* Internet connection\n* 
 A comfortable place to sit or lie down for your breathwork\n\n### Weekly\n
 \nTuesday 8pm EST\nWednesday 7am EST\nSunday 10am EST
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/high-park-yoga/events/313602466/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T152825Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T152825Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
